For fans of soccer games with a twist, Head Soccer 2022 is a must-play. This game combines the excitement of soccer with fun, over-the-top action as you compete in one-on-one matches.

Head Soccer 2022, known for its quirky characters and dynamic gameplay, has become a favorite on Fun Game. In this game, you control a player with a big head and small body, using headers and kicks to score goals against your opponent. The game features various modes, power-ups, and special moves that add to the excitement. The match ends when the time runs out, and the player with the most goals wins.

Instructions:

On your computer, use the arrow keys to move and jump, and the spacebar to kick.
